WEBVTT

00:02:10.916 --> 00:02:12.083
Act decently.

00:02:12.708 --> 00:02:13.916
Or I will tell the doctor.

00:02:14.291 --> 00:02:15.666
Do you still have a stomachache?

00:02:15.833 --> 00:02:19.375
Yes, I went to the restroom twice.

00:02:31.375 --> 00:02:32.291
Sing-sing.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.041
Hi, Man.

00:02:36.250 --> 00:02:37.708
My cousin, how are you?

00:02:37.833 --> 00:02:39.708
I am an experienced police officer.

00:02:39.791 --> 00:02:41.791
To me, this minor injury is
just like having whiteheads.

00:02:41.875 --> 00:02:42.833
But he is different.

00:02:42.916 --> 00:02:45.166
He never had a chance to work
with a superior like me.

00:02:45.416 --> 00:02:48.333
You're not my superior
and you're no longer a police officer.

00:02:48.416 --> 00:02:49.958
You've been suspended by the department.

00:02:50.041 --> 00:02:52.500
I am just protecting you like a witness.

00:02:52.708 --> 00:02:54.708
I was framed.

00:02:54.833 --> 00:02:56.333
The truth will come out sooner or later.

00:02:56.416 --> 00:02:58.041
When I resume duty, you will regret it.

00:02:58.208 --> 00:03:01.625
Stop it, don't argue anymore.

00:03:02.166 --> 00:03:03.833
Tell him to have more ambition.

00:03:03.916 --> 00:03:05.666
-For example, go undercover.
-All right.

00:03:06.333 --> 00:03:07.291
Undercover?

00:03:07.625 --> 00:03:09.041
Don't ask him to go undercover again!

00:03:09.166 --> 00:03:10.833
I hate undercover cops the most.

00:03:12.833 --> 00:03:15.958
Sing-sing, you promised me
you'd never go undercover again.

00:03:16.041 --> 00:03:18.708
Yes, but I'd rather go undercover
than protect this scumbag.

00:03:18.833 --> 00:03:20.625
With my abilities,
why would I need your protection?

00:03:20.708 --> 00:03:23.291
But you were attacked over 30 times
after you got suspended.

00:03:23.375 --> 00:03:24.375
-What?
-Come on.

00:03:24.458 --> 00:03:27.750
Stop arguing! I will give you some soup.

00:03:29.791 --> 00:03:31.375
How do you feel? Any problems?

00:03:31.750 --> 00:03:33.500
I have a headache and I feel a bit dizzy.

00:03:33.583 --> 00:03:36.250
No wonder you've been refusing
to leave the hospital.

00:03:36.416 --> 00:03:38.333
The nurse here is very pretty.

00:03:42.125 --> 00:03:43.250
I burned my hand.

00:03:43.375 --> 00:03:45.333
Miss, when can I leave the hospital?

00:03:45.583 --> 00:03:46.958
Stop looking!

00:03:47.041 --> 00:03:48.625
You don't even care that I burned my hand!

00:03:48.708 --> 00:03:50.333
Go and rub some medicine on it.

00:03:51.083 --> 00:03:53.000
-Stop looking!
-Who's looking?

00:04:08.750 --> 00:04:09.666
What are you doing?

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:12.000
-It was dangerous, didn't you see?
-What are you talking about?

00:04:12.083 --> 00:04:13.750
-Are you a pervert?
-Stay down!

00:04:15.291 --> 00:04:16.958
-Hey, that's enough!
-No, he--

00:04:17.041 --> 00:04:18.958
Don't think I'm a pushover.
Try again if you dare!

00:04:22.250 --> 00:04:23.750
Be careful!

00:04:25.375 --> 00:04:26.458
You're a pervert!

00:04:28.250 --> 00:04:29.875
I will remember you!

00:04:50.250 --> 00:04:52.125
Control, I am Chow Sing-sing.
Did you call me?

00:04:52.291 --> 00:04:53.458
-Yes.
-Good.

00:04:53.541 --> 00:04:55.833
I've just destroyed
a notorious group of killers

00:04:55.958 --> 00:04:57.833
and arrested the criminals involved.

00:04:57.916 --> 00:04:58.916
Come and lock them up.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.375
-Tell him I helped too.
-Officer Lai told you to come now.

00:05:01.750 --> 00:05:03.375
I am protecting a witness, I can't leave.

00:05:03.458 --> 00:05:05.666
Officer Lai told you to leave everything
and come now.

00:05:05.791 --> 00:05:07.333
-Leave everything?
-Yes.

00:05:07.416 --> 00:05:08.375
Okay, over.

00:05:08.625 --> 00:05:09.708
Hey.

00:05:10.125 --> 00:05:11.666
Don't move. Let me pick up the gun first.

00:05:16.291 --> 00:05:17.416
Where is Sing-sing?

00:05:17.500 --> 00:05:19.000
Everyone, face the wall now!

00:05:19.708 --> 00:05:20.791
What happened?

00:05:21.791 --> 00:05:23.291
The headquarters called him.

00:05:28.791 --> 00:05:31.458
Hey, this test tube is leaking.
Give me a cup instead.

00:05:31.583 --> 00:05:32.458
Okay.

00:05:36.708 --> 00:05:37.958
I'll take it to the lab now.

00:05:38.333 --> 00:05:39.625
What's the situation?

00:05:39.833 --> 00:05:41.125
It's a homicide.

00:05:44.958 --> 00:05:46.833
Is the victim a man or an animal?

00:05:46.916 --> 00:05:47.750
A man.

00:05:47.916 --> 00:05:50.541
Why does he have a tail?

00:05:51.333 --> 00:05:53.166
Hey, aren't you a chemistry teacher?

00:05:53.416 --> 00:05:54.333
Who are you?

00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:57.750
I'm Chow Sing-sing, you taught me
chemistry in the first movie.

00:05:58.083 --> 00:05:59.708
I don't remember ever teaching chemistry.

00:05:59.791 --> 00:06:01.041
I'm the legal medical examiner.

00:06:01.125 --> 00:06:02.500
Who are you?

00:06:02.875 --> 00:06:03.875
Chow Sing-sing.

00:06:04.041 --> 00:06:06.083
-What did you ask me just now?
-Nothing.

00:06:06.166 --> 00:06:07.458
You're just here to make trouble.

00:06:08.083 --> 00:06:10.416
-Have you seen Officer Lai?
-Which one are you talking about?

00:06:10.583 --> 00:06:13.458
That scumbag who claims to be
Dirty Harry Clint Eastwood.

00:06:13.541 --> 00:06:15.875
His nickname is Dominant Lai.

00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:18.166
You're stepping on
that scumbag's foot now.

00:06:21.166 --> 00:06:22.125
Are you hurt?

00:06:22.291 --> 00:06:24.208
Is it cool to be stepped on in public?

00:06:24.291 --> 00:06:25.208
Yes.

00:06:25.375 --> 00:06:27.083
About the homicide...

00:06:27.250 --> 00:06:28.750
This homicide is very cruel.

00:06:28.916 --> 00:06:30.708
The victim is a rich man
named Million Wong.

00:06:30.791 --> 00:06:33.208
His hands were tied to the bed
and he was stabbed with an ice pick.

00:06:33.291 --> 00:06:35.166
There was semen left on the bedsheet.

00:06:35.250 --> 00:06:37.708
The way he was killed is similar
to a scene in a recent movie.

00:06:37.875 --> 00:06:39.791
Why did you ask me
to come here so urgently?

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:41.250
Take a look at this picture first.

00:06:43.916 --> 00:06:45.458
Hey, why did you
take my picture in secret?

00:06:45.541 --> 00:06:46.583
I hate that.

00:06:46.791 --> 00:06:49.291
This is the picture of the victim.
You two look exactly the same.

00:06:49.458 --> 00:06:51.833
-But he had a mole.
-How can this be?

00:06:52.125 --> 00:06:53.291
What do you want?

00:06:53.583 --> 00:06:55.208
I have something good for you.

00:06:59.916 --> 00:07:01.500
-I'm sorry, I'll wipe your face.
-Hey.

00:07:01.750 --> 00:07:03.000
Where did you get the tissue from?

00:07:03.208 --> 00:07:04.541
It was next to the bed.

00:07:04.791 --> 00:07:07.125
-The victim used that to wipe himself.
-Wipe what?

00:07:07.291 --> 00:07:08.166
What do you think?

00:07:09.458 --> 00:07:11.291
It's all right, just treat it as a facial.

00:07:11.791 --> 00:07:13.083
Am I right, Officer Lai?

00:07:14.125 --> 00:07:15.750
Where is the cup with the victim's semen?

00:07:15.916 --> 00:07:16.916
Here it is.

00:07:17.625 --> 00:07:19.000
Why is it empty?

00:07:26.458 --> 00:07:27.500
Young man,

00:07:27.583 --> 00:07:30.458
do you know that it's a serious crime
to destroy evidence?

00:07:30.791 --> 00:07:34.083
Unless you obey my instructions,
or you'll be demoted.

00:07:36.708 --> 00:07:40.041
Your mission is to pretend to be
Million Wong and go to his home

00:07:40.375 --> 00:07:42.000
to keep an eye on his wife, Judy Tong,

00:07:42.166 --> 00:07:44.958
and his friend Tailor Lam,
who always took advantage of him.

00:07:45.083 --> 00:07:46.750
They are the most likely suspects.

00:07:46.958 --> 00:07:49.791
You want me to go undercover then?

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:53.500
The actual terms
could be whistleblower, snitch,

00:07:53.583 --> 00:07:56.916
outsider, informer, or betrayer.

00:08:00.166 --> 00:08:01.416
I'm begging you,

00:08:01.583 --> 00:08:03.583
don't make me go undercover.

00:08:03.666 --> 00:08:06.041
I promised my girlfriend
I won't go undercover anymore.

00:08:06.208 --> 00:08:08.291
Otherwise, I will lose a wife.

00:08:10.333 --> 00:08:11.833
Please be merciful.

00:08:12.125 --> 00:08:16.125
Please show mercy to me
like you would to Beggar So, sir.

00:08:18.916 --> 00:08:20.125
You can refuse to go.

00:08:20.666 --> 00:08:22.000
Find someone to get his statement.

00:08:22.083 --> 00:08:23.958
An officer intentionally destroyed
important evidence.

00:08:28.375 --> 00:08:29.625
You're so fierce.

00:08:29.916 --> 00:08:31.750
Are you trying to scare me?

00:08:32.708 --> 00:08:37.000
Even if I refuse,
another person would be willing to go.

00:08:37.708 --> 00:08:41.208
I'll just do whatever you want.

00:08:41.291 --> 00:08:42.500
You're so annoying.

00:08:44.541 --> 00:08:47.000
Madonna also begged me eight times
and I didn't give in to her,

00:08:47.125 --> 00:08:48.000
let alone to you.

00:08:48.125 --> 00:08:49.875
-You mean McDonald's?
-Madonna.

00:08:50.250 --> 00:08:51.916
Just do me a favor
and excuse me from this.

00:08:52.041 --> 00:08:53.500
No, you must go.

00:08:53.666 --> 00:08:54.791
You are too dominant!

00:08:54.875 --> 00:08:56.833
Dominant Lai is my nickname,
don't you know?

00:08:57.166 --> 00:08:59.916
Damn it, don't be such a bully in life!

00:09:00.500 --> 00:09:02.208
I am an expert in Tiger Crane

00:09:02.416 --> 00:09:05.416
and I have over ten years of experience
of Shadowless Fist and Skeleton Kick!

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:08.791
Even if I don't move my limbs,
I can kill you with my tongue.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:10.625
Do you really need me to go?

00:09:12.416 --> 00:09:15.291
Well, you must have your reasons
to make me go undercover.

00:09:15.958 --> 00:09:17.958
After much consideration,

00:09:18.041 --> 00:09:19.583
I'll respect your decision.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:21.416
-Okay?
-Okay.

00:09:22.208 --> 00:09:24.833
Actually, I love the term "whistleblower".

00:09:25.791 --> 00:09:27.625
Remember, I didn't force you.

00:09:27.791 --> 00:09:30.041
You are silly. We're on the same side.

00:09:30.125 --> 00:09:32.333
-How could you say that? Gosh.
-Right?

00:09:32.500 --> 00:09:33.875
Do you take me as a friend?

00:09:34.125 --> 00:09:35.125
We're colleagues.

00:09:35.208 --> 00:09:37.083
Lend me a few hundred thousand
to buy a flat.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:40.916
I can tell that you're not a loyal friend.

00:09:41.541 --> 00:09:43.875
I'll support you no matter what.
Work hard to solve the case.

00:09:43.958 --> 00:09:45.250
My future cousin-in-law.

00:09:45.625 --> 00:09:47.250
It's nice to see you.

00:09:47.333 --> 00:09:50.125
I'll buy you tea,
but lend me 20,000 dollars first.

00:09:50.416 --> 00:09:52.750
You've already been suspended.
How dare you borrow money again?

00:09:52.833 --> 00:09:53.916
Don't embarrass me.

00:09:54.458 --> 00:09:56.541
Can't I report a crime?
I was indecently touched by a woman.

00:09:56.625 --> 00:09:57.875
Hold it. Hey.

00:09:58.083 --> 00:09:59.875
You said you'd support me
no matter what, right?

00:10:00.041 --> 00:10:01.541
Yes, as long as you go on this mission.

00:10:01.625 --> 00:10:04.208
Great, I want him to be my assistant.

00:10:14.958 --> 00:10:16.750
The fourth seat in the third row.

00:10:26.916 --> 00:10:28.166
Do you need to be so scared?

00:10:28.250 --> 00:10:29.291
It's none of your business.

00:10:29.791 --> 00:10:31.791
Hey. Why are you so late?

00:10:32.500 --> 00:10:33.916
I was busy at the station.

00:10:34.166 --> 00:10:35.916
What's happening in the movie now?

00:10:36.208 --> 00:10:39.375
The woman is with the man on the bed.

00:10:39.666 --> 00:10:42.125
She is killing the man with an ice pick.

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:46.875
Hey, I want to tell you something.

00:10:47.041 --> 00:10:48.000
What is it?

00:10:48.166 --> 00:10:49.791
I quit my job at the school.

00:10:49.958 --> 00:10:52.958
I plan to help my mom
with her flower shop.

00:10:56.500 --> 00:11:01.375
Well, I hope to get orders
from hotels and restaurants.

00:11:01.625 --> 00:11:03.666
-What do you think?
-Good, very good.

00:11:04.208 --> 00:11:06.041
-I want to tell you something too.
-What is it?

00:11:06.208 --> 00:11:07.791
I will go undercover again
starting tomorrow.

00:11:10.250 --> 00:11:11.416
What did you say?

00:11:11.708 --> 00:11:13.708
I said I will go undercover again
starting tomorrow.

00:11:14.458 --> 00:11:16.333
-Aren't you tired of that?
-I am.

00:11:16.500 --> 00:11:18.250
But my boss isn't. I have no choice.

00:11:21.208 --> 00:11:22.833
Who will you be this time?

00:11:23.125 --> 00:11:24.625
A husband of a woman.

00:11:26.166 --> 00:11:27.833
Which woman?

00:11:29.958 --> 00:11:31.250
Keep this a secret.

00:11:31.916 --> 00:11:34.875
Judy Tong, who always appears
in gossip magazines.

00:11:35.208 --> 00:11:37.708
That's all I can tell you.
The rest is confidential.

00:11:37.791 --> 00:11:39.083
You don't mind, right?

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:44.916
Do you need to be so scared
or are you taking advantage of me?

00:11:45.166 --> 00:11:47.666
I definitely want to take advantage,
Miss Snow White!

00:11:48.583 --> 00:11:49.916
Enjoy, I'm leaving.

00:11:50.500 --> 00:11:51.750
-Hey.
-Excuse me.

00:11:51.833 --> 00:11:52.708
Man.

00:11:53.750 --> 00:11:54.583
Hey.

00:11:56.791 --> 00:11:57.666
Man.

00:11:58.041 --> 00:11:58.916
Hey.

00:11:59.250 --> 00:12:00.708
-Where are you going?
-What are you doing?

00:12:00.791 --> 00:12:01.958
Where are you going?

00:12:02.166 --> 00:12:03.000
Hey.

00:12:03.125 --> 00:12:05.166
You promised me
you won't go undercover again.

00:12:05.250 --> 00:12:06.250
You're not trustworthy!

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:09.000
You silly girl.
This is an order, I can't help it.

00:12:09.791 --> 00:12:11.666
Tomorrow is Lunar New Year's Eve.

00:12:11.750 --> 00:12:12.791
You promised to have dinner

00:12:12.875 --> 00:12:13.875
-with my family.
-Excuse me.

00:12:13.958 --> 00:12:15.250
No, go and piss again.

00:12:15.666 --> 00:12:18.208
I just won't be there,
but the food will be as delicious.

00:12:18.458 --> 00:12:20.000
-Be good.
-Okay.

00:12:20.333 --> 00:12:22.375
You want to be the husband of Judy Tong?

00:12:22.541 --> 00:12:24.708
She is androgynous and weird.

00:12:24.791 --> 00:12:26.333
Will you sleep with her on the same bed?

00:12:26.541 --> 00:12:27.583
I'm going there to work.

00:12:27.750 --> 00:12:29.750
I will never do that!

00:12:30.125 --> 00:12:31.916
But if I get drunk,
I don't know what will happen.

00:12:33.083 --> 00:12:34.541
You're going to sleep with her?

00:12:34.875 --> 00:12:36.583
I will date other men in return.

00:12:38.125 --> 00:12:39.041
You're unreasonable.

00:12:39.125 --> 00:12:40.666
You think I want to do this? It's my job.

00:12:40.750 --> 00:12:42.208
-Excuse me.
-No!

00:12:42.375 --> 00:12:44.500
-I've already pissed again.
-Go take a dump then.

00:12:44.583 --> 00:12:45.500
I don't care.

00:12:45.875 --> 00:12:48.083
If you cheat on me,

00:12:48.250 --> 00:12:50.041
I will do ten times worse than
what you did.

00:12:50.250 --> 00:12:52.791
If you sleep with one woman,
I'll sleep with ten men.

00:12:53.916 --> 00:12:57.000
As my girlfriend,
how could you say that to me?

00:12:57.083 --> 00:12:58.250
It's not only that.

00:12:58.500 --> 00:13:00.041
If you cheat on me,

00:13:00.125 --> 00:13:02.333
I'll do what the female lead did.

00:13:02.666 --> 00:13:05.166
While you're asleep,
I will tie you to the bed

00:13:05.333 --> 00:13:06.916
and stab you to death with an ice pick!

00:13:10.333 --> 00:13:12.583
Tie me to the bed? Stop joking.

00:13:12.875 --> 00:13:14.791
Caution is the parent of safety.

00:13:17.541 --> 00:13:18.791
What are you doing?

00:13:19.083 --> 00:13:20.000
Nothing.

00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:23.208
-You're done showering?
-Yes.

00:13:24.916 --> 00:13:26.541
You should write
the spring greetings first.

00:13:27.041 --> 00:13:29.958
-Fine, I'll do it tomorrow.
-No, do it now.

00:13:31.083 --> 00:13:33.666
BE PROSPEROUS

00:13:33.750 --> 00:13:36.375
HARDSHIP WILL BE OVERCOME

00:13:40.291 --> 00:13:42.166
My hand is tired.

00:13:42.333 --> 00:13:43.875
Are these fine for now?

00:13:44.041 --> 00:13:45.625
You can use your foot then.

00:13:49.916 --> 00:13:51.666
Incredible.
You really wrote with your foot.

00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:53.125
Of course, don't think I'm dumb.

00:13:53.416 --> 00:13:54.708
You're amazing.

00:13:55.250 --> 00:13:58.416
Do you love me more and more then?

00:13:59.208 --> 00:14:00.875
If you're really so amazing,

00:14:00.958 --> 00:14:02.750
eat noodles with your foot then.

00:14:07.208 --> 00:14:08.250
What did you say?

00:14:17.875 --> 00:14:18.833
Hello.

00:14:19.375 --> 00:14:21.708
Hello, is this Mrs. Wong?
I'm calling from the police station.

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:24.125
We found your husband, Million Wong,
in the New Territories.

00:14:24.500 --> 00:14:26.125
Really? Where is he now?

00:14:26.625 --> 00:14:28.875
In the police station.
Come and pick him up.

00:14:29.166 --> 00:14:30.166
Thank you.

00:14:33.958 --> 00:14:37.416
Mrs. Wong, someone sent you
some expensive underwear.

00:14:37.708 --> 00:14:40.375
Idiot, everyone knows
that I don't wear underwear.

00:14:40.541 --> 00:14:42.041
-You can have them.
-Okay.

00:14:42.541 --> 00:14:45.291
-I'm going to pick up Mr. Wong now.
-Okay, madam.

00:14:52.041 --> 00:14:53.250
Are you Jelly Tong, no...

00:14:53.416 --> 00:14:54.500
Are you Judy Tong?

00:14:57.708 --> 00:14:58.875
Call me Judy.

00:15:00.416 --> 00:15:01.625
Have you found my husband?

00:15:01.708 --> 00:15:03.750
Yes, we found him in the New Territories.

00:15:03.916 --> 00:15:05.291
He seems to be in a confused state.

00:15:05.375 --> 00:15:07.083
We suspect he experienced trauma
to his head.

00:15:07.166 --> 00:15:08.666
He doesn't have any money on him.

00:15:08.750 --> 00:15:10.125
Maybe he was robbed.

00:15:10.666 --> 00:15:12.291
By woman, I suppose.

00:15:14.791 --> 00:15:16.458
Don't any of you smoke?

00:15:17.250 --> 00:15:19.708
I am sorry, Mrs. Wong.
Smoking is not allowed in this room.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:21.375
Would you put me in jail then?

00:15:22.083 --> 00:15:23.375
No.

00:15:23.541 --> 00:15:24.833
But you'll be fined 5,000 dollars.

00:15:25.625 --> 00:15:27.583
Here is 10,000 dollars.
I will treat you to a cigarette.

00:15:28.666 --> 00:15:30.833
Mrs. Wong, money is not everything
in the world.

00:15:33.083 --> 00:15:34.250
It isn't.

00:15:34.500 --> 00:15:36.375
But you're doomed if you don't have money.

00:16:03.083 --> 00:16:04.125
You're not my husband.

00:16:04.208 --> 00:16:05.625
I didn't say I was.

00:16:05.875 --> 00:16:07.625
He is obviously your husband.

00:16:07.708 --> 00:16:08.916
I'm not acknowledging him.

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:11.000
You fooled around
until you're in a confused state.

00:16:12.083 --> 00:16:13.500
Hey, say something.

00:16:13.958 --> 00:16:16.458
What could I say?
I don't remember anything.

00:16:16.875 --> 00:16:18.291
She is your wife.

00:16:18.458 --> 00:16:19.375
No.

00:16:19.750 --> 00:16:22.375
I didn't say you were.

00:16:22.458 --> 00:16:24.541
You are a couple. You fight and reconcile.

00:16:24.708 --> 00:16:26.250
Say nice things to her and you'll be fine.

00:16:26.333 --> 00:16:28.666
I won't go home with him.
I came to see if he was dead or not.

00:16:28.916 --> 00:16:31.125
I have a faint memory
of having a pretty wife.

00:16:31.250 --> 00:16:32.416
Isn't she pretty?

00:16:32.583 --> 00:16:33.666
What do you think?

00:16:33.833 --> 00:16:36.125
Although she is not pretty,
she really is your wife.

00:16:36.458 --> 00:16:38.000
I am sorry, police can't tell lies.

00:16:38.208 --> 00:16:40.291
I heard my wife has a nice figure.

00:16:40.416 --> 00:16:41.541
Doesn't she have a nice figure?

00:16:41.666 --> 00:16:43.375
My wife doesn't wear underwear.

00:16:43.458 --> 00:16:45.291
I peeked earlier. She's not wearing one.

00:16:46.916 --> 00:16:48.333
I'm just guessing.

00:16:49.125 --> 00:16:51.666
You bastard,
you haven't completely gone crazy.

00:16:51.833 --> 00:16:54.583
You have a sharp tongue!
I don't know whether to laugh or cry.

00:16:55.333 --> 00:16:57.916
Yes, go home and decide
whether to laugh or cry.

00:16:58.041 --> 00:16:59.250
Are you telling me what to do?

00:16:59.666 --> 00:17:01.541
I've been enduring you.
What kind of attitude is that?

00:17:01.625 --> 00:17:03.250
You reported
that your husband went missing.

00:17:03.333 --> 00:17:04.875
You give an attitude now that he's found.

00:17:04.958 --> 00:17:06.625
Should we take you to Shenzhen?

00:17:06.791 --> 00:17:09.583
Did you know we can lock you up
in Shenzhen for a year without a trial?

00:17:10.500 --> 00:17:12.833
What are you looking at?
You're rude. Look at me.

00:17:13.166 --> 00:17:14.166
How long can he protect you?

00:17:14.250 --> 00:17:16.125
In July 1997, I'll arrest him too.

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:17.583
Who are you?

00:17:18.000 --> 00:17:19.708
I'm a police officer from China.

00:17:20.291 --> 00:17:22.875
You look familiar.
When did you go to China?

00:17:23.166 --> 00:17:24.291
I didn't.

00:17:24.625 --> 00:17:25.583
You didn't?

00:17:25.958 --> 00:17:28.333
You look like a criminal who steals money
from various governments.

00:17:28.416 --> 00:17:30.083
Buddy, get me a car.

00:17:30.166 --> 00:17:31.708
I want to take them with me,
including her.

00:17:31.791 --> 00:17:32.708
Me?

00:17:33.500 --> 00:17:34.458
Don't interrupt.

00:17:34.541 --> 00:17:36.500
Are you going to cooperate?
You want to destroy peace?

00:17:36.583 --> 00:17:38.291
Do you want me to arrest your mother?

00:17:39.791 --> 00:17:41.208
Good thing it's my mother, not me.

00:17:41.375 --> 00:17:44.166
Are you done? Damn mother.
I'm very sleepy.

00:17:44.333 --> 00:17:46.166
Don't be ridiculous, I'm not your mother.

00:17:46.625 --> 00:17:48.500
Go home if you feel sleepy.
Come home with me.

00:17:48.583 --> 00:17:49.791
-Don't go.
-Let's go.

00:17:49.875 --> 00:17:51.125
Hey, where is my gun?

00:17:51.208 --> 00:17:53.291
Isn't it good that they left? Let them go.

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:56.208
Bullshit works, young man.

00:17:56.916 --> 00:17:58.125
How dare you call me that?

00:17:58.291 --> 00:17:59.583
You're already suspended.

00:17:59.666 --> 00:18:01.291
If you pose as a cop again,
we'll arrest you.

00:18:01.375 --> 00:18:02.416
-Hey, don't be so bad.
-What?

00:18:02.500 --> 00:18:03.791
I posed as a Chinese police officer.

00:18:03.875 --> 00:18:05.083
-Let them arrest me.
-You--

00:18:05.166 --> 00:18:07.458
Stop or I will really apply
to be a Chinese police officer

00:18:07.708 --> 00:18:09.708
and cut your mother's pork in 1997.

00:18:11.875 --> 00:18:13.625
Good thing my mother is a vegetarian.

00:18:20.458 --> 00:18:21.625
-Mr. Wong.
-Mr. Wong.

00:18:33.375 --> 00:18:34.875
Why are you so amazed? This is your house.

00:18:34.958 --> 00:18:36.083
I lost my memory.

00:18:36.166 --> 00:18:37.250
So what?

00:18:37.333 --> 00:18:39.083
That's not what I mean.

00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:42.083
Do you know who she is?

00:18:45.208 --> 00:18:46.208
Mom?

00:18:46.291 --> 00:18:47.875
Mr. Wong, why did you call me that?

00:18:48.375 --> 00:18:51.250
Damn it, Toirepepa is
our Japanese housekeeper.

00:18:51.333 --> 00:18:52.625
-What? Toilet paper?
-That's right.

00:18:52.916 --> 00:18:54.250
-Right.
-It's a Japanese name.

00:18:54.583 --> 00:18:55.416
-Right.
-Dad.

00:18:56.833 --> 00:18:57.833
Dad.

00:18:58.583 --> 00:18:59.750
-My dear son.
-Dad.

00:18:59.833 --> 00:19:01.083
I missed you so much!

00:19:01.166 --> 00:19:02.250
Damn you!

00:19:02.333 --> 00:19:03.708
He is the son of the gardener.

00:19:04.166 --> 00:19:06.125
-He called me Dad.
-He calls everyone Dad.

00:19:06.208 --> 00:19:09.125
-Greet everyone.
-Dad.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:13.916
-I'm glad you're back.
-Do you know who he is?

00:19:14.083 --> 00:19:15.916
-Does he cook curry?
-He is your dad.

00:19:16.083 --> 00:19:16.958
What?

00:19:17.041 --> 00:19:19.583
-Good boy.
-Dad.

00:19:21.666 --> 00:19:23.750
-It's good to see you again.
-Do you know who he is?

00:19:23.833 --> 00:19:25.958
-Maybe he's the gardener or something.
-He's your nanny.

00:19:26.125 --> 00:19:27.583
What?

00:19:27.666 --> 00:19:30.250
-Mr. Wong, do you want to have some milk?
-I'm not thirsty, maybe later.

00:19:33.375 --> 00:19:34.625
Do you know who he is?

00:19:34.833 --> 00:19:36.416
-Don't tell me he's my brother.
-That's right.

00:19:36.500 --> 00:19:38.333
-What?
-You treat him as your brother.

00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:39.666
I see.

00:19:40.666 --> 00:19:42.666
Call his name
or he will come and bite you.

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:43.750
No way.

00:19:43.833 --> 00:19:45.916
-What is his name?
-Use your brain!

00:19:46.333 --> 00:19:48.375
Hey. Dolly...

00:19:49.875 --> 00:19:52.333
David, Peter, Maria, Rose, Gigo,

00:19:52.500 --> 00:19:54.583
Giorgio Armani, Valentino, Balenciaga,

00:19:54.750 --> 00:19:56.666
Wong Jing, Ng Man Tat, Gordon Chan!

00:20:05.291 --> 00:20:07.166
That dog should be euthanized.

00:20:07.416 --> 00:20:09.250
His name is Dolly Law!

00:20:09.416 --> 00:20:11.250
-You forgot his name.
-Hey.

00:20:11.333 --> 00:20:13.208
I called him Dolly many times.

00:20:13.375 --> 00:20:15.333
It's Dolly Law, not Dolly.

00:20:15.458 --> 00:20:16.583
You forgot "Law".

00:20:17.666 --> 00:20:19.541
That's why he kept chasing after me.

00:20:19.625 --> 00:20:20.583
Mr. Wong.

00:20:20.958 --> 00:20:23.083
-The vet has arrived.
-Which dog should I draw teeth from?

00:20:23.166 --> 00:20:24.208
This way.

00:20:24.375 --> 00:20:25.750
Thank you, doctor.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.916
Lower your voice.

00:20:51.333 --> 00:20:52.250
Hey.

00:20:52.416 --> 00:20:54.166
You always fall asleep
when having a massage.

00:20:54.250 --> 00:20:55.291
Why are you so excited today?

00:20:56.583 --> 00:20:58.000
I don't know why.

00:20:59.541 --> 00:21:02.916
-Hey, do you need to do that?
-Mr. Wong, you love it.

00:21:03.125 --> 00:21:04.666
-Really?
-Yes.

00:21:04.750 --> 00:21:05.666
Forget it then.

00:21:14.041 --> 00:21:17.458
Why are you so interested
in this old picture?

00:21:17.875 --> 00:21:19.750
-I lost my memory.
-So what?

00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:21.333
I mean,

00:21:21.416 --> 00:21:24.625
I was wondering why I was wearing boxers
to take a picture.

00:21:24.708 --> 00:21:26.416
That's so strange.

00:21:26.708 --> 00:21:30.250
You know, I convinced you for so long
before you wore any underwear.

00:21:30.416 --> 00:21:33.000
You refused to wear anything at first.
You wanted to look sexy.

00:21:33.208 --> 00:21:34.583
Look at how dissatisfied you look.

00:21:35.833 --> 00:21:37.583
I didn't expect him
to be that kind of person.

00:21:37.791 --> 00:21:38.916
What?

00:21:39.416 --> 00:21:41.541
I don't remember being
that kind of person.

00:21:42.750 --> 00:21:45.375
If not for your looks,
I'd suspect that you're an impostor.

00:21:45.583 --> 00:21:48.708
An impostor? I told you I lost my memory.

00:21:48.791 --> 00:21:50.583
Did I say or do anything
before I went missing?

00:21:50.666 --> 00:21:52.250
Who knows what you said or did?

00:21:52.666 --> 00:21:53.833
Toirepepa.

00:21:53.916 --> 00:21:55.791
-Why are you calling her?
-To prepare your bath.

00:21:55.916 --> 00:21:57.083
She's sleeping.

00:21:58.083 --> 00:21:59.833
What can I do for you, Mr. Wong?

00:21:59.916 --> 00:22:01.458
You always move so quietly.

00:22:01.541 --> 00:22:04.291
-Mrs. Wong, he said I move quietly.
-Everybody is the same

00:22:04.375 --> 00:22:05.416
in this house.

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:08.125
You're not the only one
who knows how to move quietly.

00:22:17.208 --> 00:22:19.458
-You want a beating? Hello?
-Pretending to be dead?

00:22:19.708 --> 00:22:22.500
Hello, Officer Lai. I am Judy Tong.

00:22:22.833 --> 00:22:23.916
-What can I do for you?
-Speak!

00:22:24.000 --> 00:22:26.083
The person you found is not my husband.

00:22:26.208 --> 00:22:27.083
Make it thinner.

00:22:27.791 --> 00:22:29.083
How do you know that?

00:22:29.250 --> 00:22:30.583
He doesn't know anybody.

00:22:30.666 --> 00:22:33.250
He thought the gardener's son was his
and he was bitten by our dog.

00:22:33.333 --> 00:22:36.625
I asked him to shower and he really did!

00:22:36.875 --> 00:22:38.541
He only did it four times a year before.

00:22:38.791 --> 00:22:41.500
When we got married, I begged him
for a week and he still wouldn't shower.

00:22:42.291 --> 00:22:44.916
We made him shower in the detention center
and he got addicted to it.

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.875
Hey, he really is your husband.

00:22:47.041 --> 00:22:49.750
Treat him nicely.
Otherwise, I won't let you off easily.

00:22:50.208 --> 00:22:52.041
How could you say that?
Are you really Officer Lai?

00:22:52.125 --> 00:22:53.666
If I'm not Officer Lai,
then am I Leon Lai?

00:22:54.291 --> 00:22:55.333
Go to hell.

00:22:55.875 --> 00:22:57.583
That doesn't sound like your voice.

00:22:57.666 --> 00:22:59.458
That voice wasn't mine.

00:22:59.791 --> 00:23:01.083
You want to be beaten up?

00:23:06.875 --> 00:23:07.833
Officer Chan.

00:23:07.916 --> 00:23:09.708
Mrs. Wong, what can I do for you?

00:23:13.375 --> 00:23:15.041
I don't think my husband is my husband.

00:23:15.208 --> 00:23:16.750
I don't understand. Please explain.

00:23:16.916 --> 00:23:18.708
Officer Lai found my missing husband.

00:23:18.791 --> 00:23:19.958
He looks exactly like my husband.

00:23:20.083 --> 00:23:21.041
But when we got home,

00:23:21.208 --> 00:23:23.666
I noticed that he is
not my husband at all.

00:23:23.916 --> 00:23:26.333
Officer Lai found your husband
who looks exactly like your husband.

00:23:26.416 --> 00:23:28.333
But you noticed
that he isn't your husband.

00:23:28.458 --> 00:23:29.625
He is not my husband at all.

00:23:30.208 --> 00:23:32.458
So you suspect that
your husband's look-alike

00:23:32.541 --> 00:23:33.500
is not your husband.

00:23:33.958 --> 00:23:34.958
More or less.

00:23:35.041 --> 00:23:36.416
Then you should talk to Officer Lai.

00:23:36.833 --> 00:23:38.083
I called him,

00:23:38.208 --> 00:23:39.958
but there was a fake Officer Lai.

00:23:40.041 --> 00:23:42.416
He told me that my look-alike husband
is my husband.

00:23:43.583 --> 00:23:45.750
That fake Officer Lai pretended
to be him and told you

00:23:45.875 --> 00:23:48.000
that your look-alike husband
is your real husband.

00:23:48.375 --> 00:23:50.416
-More or less.
-I have a suggestion.

00:23:50.583 --> 00:23:53.416
Go home, take a warm bath,
and drink a glass of hot milk.

00:23:53.583 --> 00:23:55.000
See Officer Lai tomorrow morning.

00:23:55.083 --> 00:23:56.875
Then you will discover
that your look-alike husband

00:23:56.958 --> 00:23:58.333
is your husband again.

00:23:59.083 --> 00:24:01.416
So you don't believe or trust me either.

00:24:01.583 --> 00:24:02.958
Do you think I am crazy?

00:24:03.208 --> 00:24:04.416
More or less.

00:24:04.708 --> 00:24:06.500
He really is an impostor.

00:24:06.666 --> 00:24:07.875
I am an impostor too.

00:24:10.416 --> 00:24:12.125
Actually, I am Andy Lau.

00:24:12.458 --> 00:24:14.125
It's 12:30 a.m. on Lunar New Year's Eve.

00:24:14.291 --> 00:24:15.541
Gosh, it's 1:00 a.m.

00:24:15.625 --> 00:24:18.291
-Happy New Year. Let's be prosperous.
-What are you doing, Officer Chan?

00:24:18.375 --> 00:24:19.666
-That's all, bye.
-I'm not done yet.

00:24:25.250 --> 00:24:27.833
You are great, my dear classmate.

00:24:28.083 --> 00:24:29.250
Happy New Year!

00:24:29.541 --> 00:24:30.875
I'll be in trouble because of you.

00:24:31.333 --> 00:24:33.000
She is so rich.
Do you know that she can sue us?

00:24:33.166 --> 00:24:35.583
But we are upholding justice
and maintaining the law.

00:24:35.666 --> 00:24:37.875
Now you're spreading injustice
and ignoring the law!

00:24:38.166 --> 00:24:39.958
Why did you poke me so hard? Go to hell.

00:24:41.250 --> 00:24:43.625
-What?
-I poked you and you hit me?

00:24:43.791 --> 00:24:44.750
I will kill you!

00:24:45.166 --> 00:24:46.791
Hey!

00:24:48.375 --> 00:24:50.541
Officer Chan, I left my lighter.

00:24:50.791 --> 00:24:52.208
Why do you have black eyes?

00:24:52.833 --> 00:24:54.625
I don't get enough sleep,
so I have dark circles.

00:24:54.750 --> 00:24:57.333
Mrs. Wong, Happy New Year.
I hope your dreams come true.

00:24:57.500 --> 00:25:00.416
I wish you luck, prosperity,
success in studies and eternal youth.

00:25:00.583 --> 00:25:02.875
Anyway, be happy. Happy New Year.

00:25:03.458 --> 00:25:04.750
All of you are crazy!

00:25:29.791 --> 00:25:31.166
What noise is that?

00:25:33.291 --> 00:25:34.291
What are you doing?

00:25:38.333 --> 00:25:39.333
What are you doing?

00:25:39.625 --> 00:25:41.333
-You made me your assistant.
-Yes.

00:25:41.583 --> 00:25:43.583
You told me to protect you
with a gun 24/7, right?

00:25:43.750 --> 00:25:45.291
-Yes.
-That's what I'm doing.

00:25:45.833 --> 00:25:48.166
I didn't tell you
to cut through people's ceiling, man.

00:25:48.916 --> 00:25:50.041
Yes, you didn't.

00:25:50.375 --> 00:25:51.583
Go away, you idiot.

00:25:55.958 --> 00:25:59.125
I don't need your protection here. Go.

00:25:59.666 --> 00:26:02.083
No, I have to watch you closely
and see if you'll cheat on my cousin.

00:26:02.166 --> 00:26:03.833
-Mrs. Wong, you're back.
-Yes.

00:26:09.291 --> 00:26:11.083
Judy is back, get out of here.

00:26:13.958 --> 00:26:16.458
Hey, a fat woman has gone into the room.
What shall I do?

00:26:21.666 --> 00:26:23.833
You're back? Where did you go?

00:26:24.500 --> 00:26:26.250
I just went out for wonton noodles.

00:26:26.333 --> 00:26:28.583
-Wonton noodles? Very good.
-Yes.

00:26:28.916 --> 00:26:31.833
In order to finish my mission,
I need to use my power of seduction.

00:26:31.916 --> 00:26:34.958
I will flirt with her
and make her tell me the truth.

00:26:35.208 --> 00:26:38.041
To find out the truth,
I need to use the power of my charms

00:26:38.125 --> 00:26:39.666
in order to expose his real identity.

00:27:04.958 --> 00:27:07.625
Judy!

00:27:07.833 --> 00:27:10.791
Million!

00:27:11.291 --> 00:27:12.750
Judy!

00:27:12.958 --> 00:27:14.916
Million!

00:27:45.833 --> 00:27:47.958
Sorry, I am tired today.

00:27:48.125 --> 00:27:49.875
I am going to sleep in the study room.

00:27:53.291 --> 00:27:54.875
Benevolent God,

00:27:54.958 --> 00:27:58.666
please give me a strong man in my dream.

00:27:59.458 --> 00:28:00.875
Thank you.

00:28:08.583 --> 00:28:09.958
He's really strong.

00:28:10.125 --> 00:28:11.291
And he's naked.

00:28:11.958 --> 00:28:14.166
Thank you, God.

00:28:14.250 --> 00:28:15.458
I'm coming!

00:28:15.541 --> 00:28:16.791
GOD OF PROSPERITY

00:28:18.541 --> 00:28:21.708
Hurry up, arrange the presents properly.

00:28:22.541 --> 00:28:24.750
-Mr. and Mrs. Wong are coming down.
-Mr. and Mrs. Wong!

00:28:24.916 --> 00:28:28.750
Mr. Wong, may your business thrive,
be prosperous and go smoothly for you.

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:31.625
We wish you good fortune.

00:28:31.708 --> 00:28:33.250
Here is your red envelope.

00:28:33.333 --> 00:28:35.708
-We wish you prosperity.
-Hey, you should give them some too.

00:28:35.958 --> 00:28:37.666
I didn't bring any. Give me some.

00:28:39.083 --> 00:28:39.958
Here.

00:28:40.583 --> 00:28:42.416
Here is your red envelope.

00:28:42.875 --> 00:28:43.958
-Happy New Year.
-Thank you.

00:28:44.041 --> 00:28:45.875
-Mr. Wong.
-Good fortune to you.

00:28:45.958 --> 00:28:47.833
-Thank you.
-Mr. Wong, what about me?

00:28:48.375 --> 00:28:49.916
Hey, you're married, right?

00:28:50.000 --> 00:28:51.208
-Right.
-Give it back to me.

00:28:51.291 --> 00:28:52.125
Where is yours?

00:28:52.416 --> 00:28:54.416
-Mr. Wong, I'm not married.
-You got mine.

00:28:54.500 --> 00:28:55.458
Yours is with Mrs. Wong.

00:28:55.541 --> 00:28:57.000
They're giving out two per person there!

00:28:58.791 --> 00:29:00.666
-I'm rich.
-Happy New Year.

00:29:00.833 --> 00:29:01.833
-Officer Lai.
-Hey.

00:29:01.916 --> 00:29:03.500
-This is for you.
-Officer Lai.

00:29:03.583 --> 00:29:04.958
This is very kind of you.

00:29:05.041 --> 00:29:07.166
I should since I'm visiting you.

00:29:07.250 --> 00:29:08.750
-Happy New Year, Officer Lai!
-Stop.

00:29:09.041 --> 00:29:10.125
We can't be prosperous.

