Put in 50,000 dollars.

00:45:42.750 --> 00:45:44.000
What do you think?

00:45:44.291 --> 00:45:45.458
Add 150,000 dollars.

00:45:46.333 --> 00:45:48.166
-We'll get rich with just the base fee.
-Really?

00:45:49.666 --> 00:45:50.666
Follow.

00:45:53.708 --> 00:45:55.250
Hey, show us the money.

00:45:56.291 --> 00:45:58.541
-Where is the change?
-Change?

00:45:58.833 --> 00:46:01.208
-Hey, you over there...
-Wait.

00:46:01.416 --> 00:46:03.083
I'll go and get the money, sit here.

00:46:04.666 --> 00:46:07.000
Honey, give me a few million dollars.

00:46:07.125 --> 00:46:09.416
We have always gambled with our own money.

00:46:09.708 --> 00:46:11.750
Don't you have 30 million dollars
in cash at home?

00:46:12.000 --> 00:46:13.833
I forgot where I put them.

00:46:14.416 --> 00:46:16.291
You will remember, you're smart.

00:46:16.750 --> 00:46:18.416
-Which one should I discard?
-Well...

00:46:20.583 --> 00:46:21.416
This one.

00:46:22.291 --> 00:46:23.666
-Really?
-Trust me.

00:46:25.208 --> 00:46:26.041
Nine circles.

00:46:26.125 --> 00:46:27.458
-I win!
-Me too.

00:46:27.541 --> 00:46:28.416
Three wins in one shot.

00:46:32.916 --> 00:46:33.833
Damn you!

00:46:35.000 --> 00:46:35.916
Where is Officer Lai?

00:46:36.000 --> 00:46:37.416
He is having fun inside the CID room.

00:46:43.916 --> 00:46:45.416
You bastard! You want to get beaten up?

00:46:48.500 --> 00:46:51.250
-I want to discuss something important.
-Can't you see I am beating up someone?

00:46:51.333 --> 00:46:53.291
I need two million for gambling.

00:46:53.458 --> 00:46:55.333
Two million? Are you kidding?

00:46:56.041 --> 00:46:57.083
How dare you counterattack?

00:47:00.083 --> 00:47:01.750
You must give me two million
no matter what.

00:47:03.000 --> 00:47:04.750
Where do I get two million for you?

00:47:04.916 --> 00:47:06.083
Tailor is gambling at my home.

00:47:06.166 --> 00:47:08.583
If I have no money, I'll be exposed.
Then we're doomed.

00:47:08.666 --> 00:47:10.791
-Hurry!
-Let me go first.

00:47:10.875 --> 00:47:12.166
Agree and I'll let you go.

00:47:16.750 --> 00:47:18.125
Did you go to the market?

00:47:18.750 --> 00:47:20.416
I'm sorry, I misplaced my loose change.

00:47:20.583 --> 00:47:22.166
They were in the servant's quarters,

00:47:22.250 --> 00:47:23.583
which is in Yuen Long.

00:47:23.666 --> 00:47:25.291
Cut the crap, we're waiting for you.

00:47:25.375 --> 00:47:26.958
-Deal.
-Deal.

00:47:27.208 --> 00:47:29.000
-A pair of eights, your call.
-Really?

00:47:29.083 --> 00:47:31.250
-Then I want to show--
-Wait, pretend first.

00:47:31.750 --> 00:47:34.291
Nothing special, just 200,000 dollars.

00:47:34.458 --> 00:47:35.583
Just 200,000 dollars?

00:47:36.208 --> 00:47:37.916
-I'll add 800,000 dollars.
-I will follow you!

00:47:45.708 --> 00:47:46.750
Three eights.

00:47:47.208 --> 00:47:48.500
All right, show hand.

00:47:48.583 --> 00:47:50.250
-What about the newspaper?
-Include it too.

00:47:51.250 --> 00:47:52.416
Three eights?

00:47:52.875 --> 00:47:55.250
Well, it's not much! Follow!

00:47:59.000 --> 00:47:59.833
I quit.

00:48:02.083 --> 00:48:04.458
I have three Aces. I don't believe
that you've got four eights.

00:48:06.166 --> 00:48:08.708
Don't get so excited when you win.
Don't cry, buddy!

00:48:09.166 --> 00:48:10.208
Four eights!

00:48:14.416 --> 00:48:16.500
What? I had an eight!

00:48:17.666 --> 00:48:19.333
-You mean the game before you left?
-Of course!

00:48:19.541 --> 00:48:21.041
But we played many rounds after that.

00:48:21.458 --> 00:48:22.458
Why didn't you tell me?

00:48:22.541 --> 00:48:23.916
-You didn't ask!
-I...

00:48:27.333 --> 00:48:29.166
You're back? Did you win or lose?

00:48:29.333 --> 00:48:30.416
You can tell from my head.

00:48:30.583 --> 00:48:31.583
You lost everything?

00:48:31.666 --> 00:48:33.958
-You said you were the King of Gamblers!
-When did I say that?

00:48:34.416 --> 00:48:35.416
I mentioned it.

00:48:36.416 --> 00:48:37.583
What should we do now?

00:48:37.750 --> 00:48:39.458
Give me one million to win it back.

00:48:39.625 --> 00:48:41.375
I will show them my real power
as King of Gamblers.

00:48:41.458 --> 00:48:42.833
You want one more million?

00:48:43.125 --> 00:48:46.333
I gave you all the bond
and bail money in the station.

00:48:46.541 --> 00:48:48.041
We're being asked to return the money.

00:48:48.125 --> 00:48:51.041
If you don't give it back,
you'd better leave by boat and escape.

00:48:51.125 --> 00:48:52.541
Please lend me money for the ticket.

00:48:52.625 --> 00:48:54.458
You...

00:48:54.541 --> 00:48:55.875
-Give us one million more
-You idiot!

00:48:55.958 --> 00:48:57.250
or we're all doomed.

00:48:57.916 --> 00:49:00.458
-Hey.
-What if you lose again?

00:49:01.000 --> 00:49:02.583
This is our last resort.
Let's take the risk.

00:49:02.666 --> 00:49:06.291
We're just making a living.
Why are you beating us?

00:49:06.708 --> 00:49:08.041
Who are you beating up again?

00:49:08.208 --> 00:49:09.500
Two racketeers.

00:49:10.041 --> 00:49:12.000
You're beating up
such noble professionals?

00:49:12.500 --> 00:49:14.166
He cheated someone of two dollars.

00:49:14.458 --> 00:49:15.666
Whose two dollars?

00:49:15.958 --> 00:49:18.375
-Mine.
-He even cheated a beggar?

00:49:18.458 --> 00:49:19.708
-Beat him up!
-Beat him up!

00:49:22.916 --> 00:49:24.125
What?

00:49:24.208 --> 00:49:27.000
The archenemy of the God of Gamblers,
Master Hung?

00:49:27.791 --> 00:49:28.750
Hello, how are you?

00:49:28.833 --> 00:49:30.458
I lost so much money
that I need to run away.

00:49:30.541 --> 00:49:32.458
Buddy, ask them not to beat us.

00:49:32.666 --> 00:49:35.000
I will teach you how to cheat.
You'll surely win.

00:49:35.291 --> 00:49:37.375
Sure, but give me a demo first.

00:49:47.791 --> 00:49:49.583
Are you kidding me?
He's not back yet after so long?

00:49:51.333 --> 00:49:53.166
We've finished 16 rounds
and he hasn't returned.

00:49:53.250 --> 00:49:54.083
What is he doing?

00:49:54.875 --> 00:49:56.083
He is back.

00:49:56.250 --> 00:49:58.000
Everyone...

00:50:18.625 --> 00:50:20.250
-He looks so cool!
-So cool!

00:50:31.666 --> 00:50:33.083
You look familiar,

00:50:33.333 --> 00:50:35.208
but I don't know
who you're pretending to be.

00:50:37.083 --> 00:50:37.916
Take a guess.

00:51:01.708 --> 00:51:03.583
I know! The God of Gamblers.

00:51:04.041 --> 00:51:04.875
Wrong.

00:51:05.250 --> 00:51:06.500
It's David Copperfield.

00:51:09.166 --> 00:51:10.000
Deal.

00:51:10.291 --> 00:51:11.291
I have three Kings.

00:51:11.833 --> 00:51:12.750
I have three Aces.

00:51:13.250 --> 00:51:14.083
Straight flush.

00:51:14.208 --> 00:51:15.625
Mine is better.

00:51:16.625 --> 00:51:17.458
Four Aces.

00:51:18.041 --> 00:51:18.875
Five Aces!

00:51:34.166 --> 00:51:35.666
What that person taught you really work.

00:51:35.833 --> 00:51:36.833
Win as much as you can.

00:51:37.333 --> 00:51:40.500
I'll take this opportunity to find out
the truth about Million's death.

00:51:42.791 --> 00:51:43.625
One million.

00:51:43.833 --> 00:51:44.666
I will follow.

00:51:50.083 --> 00:51:51.000
A pair of Aces, my call.

00:51:51.250 --> 00:51:53.333
Are you stupid?
The straight flush calls it.

00:51:53.541 --> 00:51:54.416
Show hand.

00:51:59.333 --> 00:52:01.000
I don't believe you're David Copperfield.

00:52:01.083 --> 00:52:02.000
I will follow.

00:52:03.166 --> 00:52:04.291
I have 50 cents left.

00:52:05.083 --> 00:52:06.250
I'll get five million as credit.

00:52:06.458 --> 00:52:09.000
Forget the money.
If you answer my question,

00:52:09.166 --> 00:52:10.666
I'll consider that you've followed.

00:52:10.833 --> 00:52:11.875
What is your question?

00:52:13.166 --> 00:52:18.166
Have you ever thought of killing me?

00:52:22.125 --> 00:52:23.291
Answer me.

00:52:26.708 --> 00:52:28.708
-I...
-Answer me!

00:52:33.083 --> 00:52:34.458
I'm done playing!

00:52:35.708 --> 00:52:37.458
Your question is ridiculous.

00:52:37.750 --> 00:52:39.041
-Let's go.
-Okay.

00:52:40.208 --> 00:52:41.500
We'll take the money if you're done.

00:52:43.166 --> 00:52:45.250
You've won the money.
Have you found out the truth?

00:52:46.041 --> 00:52:47.166
The truth is...

00:52:47.916 --> 00:52:50.000
I only had a four, but that idiot quit.

00:52:52.000 --> 00:52:54.500
-Boss, are you all right?
-Are you hurt?

00:52:55.541 --> 00:52:57.541
Give me back the money!

00:52:58.083 --> 00:52:59.041
We'll return the money.

00:52:59.208 --> 00:53:00.916
But we don't need to share
our winnings, right?

00:53:02.291 --> 00:53:03.500
Don't you need to pay interest?

00:53:04.750 --> 00:53:07.166
Pay him according to the bank's rate.

00:53:07.625 --> 00:53:09.958
The interest rate today is cheap,
just 2.75 percent.

00:53:10.458 --> 00:53:13.375
Two million divided by 365 days.

00:53:13.833 --> 00:53:14.791
It's 25 dollars.

00:53:14.875 --> 00:53:16.416
I'll give you 30 dollars. Keep the change.

00:53:16.750 --> 00:53:18.041
Give me ten dollars as a tip.

00:53:21.458 --> 00:53:23.375
We wouldn't worry if we did this earlier.

00:53:27.958 --> 00:53:29.333
Any progress on your investigation?

00:53:30.916 --> 00:53:33.333
I noticed that Judy Tong
is becoming really strange.

00:53:33.625 --> 00:53:35.791
I think she has a secret.

00:53:35.958 --> 00:53:37.583
And Tailor Lam...

00:53:37.666 --> 00:53:39.083
Don't just look at the surface.

00:53:40.291 --> 00:53:41.791
When I was training in Scotland,

00:53:42.291 --> 00:53:44.958
I studied all the extraordinary cases
in the world.

00:53:45.625 --> 00:53:47.750
Including Murder on the Orient Express,

00:53:48.125 --> 00:53:49.583
Death on the Nile,

00:53:49.833 --> 00:53:51.208
Dial M for Murder,

00:53:51.500 --> 00:53:54.500
The Hidden Corpse, and many more.

00:53:55.125 --> 00:53:56.375
I found an important principle.

00:53:56.500 --> 00:53:57.333
What is it?

00:53:57.416 --> 00:53:59.666
The most suspicious person
is less likely to be the culprit.

00:54:00.250 --> 00:54:01.083
Damn!

00:54:01.166 --> 00:54:03.083
I agree! Like in the movies,
the less suspicious person

00:54:03.166 --> 00:54:04.375
is more likely the culprit?

00:54:04.458 --> 00:54:05.708
You can say that.

00:54:06.000 --> 00:54:08.458
Maybe he pretends not to know the victim,

00:54:08.916 --> 00:54:11.833
looks ordinary, is not particularly
tall or short, very strong,

00:54:12.000 --> 00:54:14.791
has no inclination to violence,
likes to beat up people

00:54:15.291 --> 00:54:16.500
and loves money.

00:54:16.583 --> 00:54:18.208
He'll cheat people
of even 30 or 40 dollars.

00:54:18.833 --> 00:54:20.708
Based on what you said,
the murderer is you.

00:54:21.125 --> 00:54:22.333
Guys, arrest him.

00:54:24.166 --> 00:54:25.125
Are you crazy?

00:54:25.791 --> 00:54:26.666
Are you mad?

00:54:27.583 --> 00:54:28.750
It's just a theory.

00:54:29.041 --> 00:54:30.208
Going back to the topic at hand,

00:54:30.458 --> 00:54:32.791
if you can't get any clues
in Judy Tong's home,

00:54:32.875 --> 00:54:35.125
go to the office to check
if Tailor Lam and Million Wong

00:54:35.291 --> 00:54:37.708
had any conflicts in business
that may lead to his murder.

00:54:38.541 --> 00:54:40.541
You just said the most suspicious one
isn't the culprit.

00:54:40.666 --> 00:54:42.583
I'm just saying that.
Why don't you go and investigate?

00:54:43.125 --> 00:54:45.250
Let me finish the most
important thing first, okay?

00:55:08.375 --> 00:55:10.041
"I'll love you for 360 years"?

00:55:12.375 --> 00:55:14.458
Damn it, you're totally
ignoring my existence.

00:55:32.125 --> 00:55:33.541
A bitch and a bastard.

00:55:34.250 --> 00:55:36.166
A bitch and a bastard.

00:55:40.958 --> 00:55:42.166
I want to kill them!

00:55:42.875 --> 00:55:43.833
Where's the knife?

00:55:48.958 --> 00:55:50.000
Fuck!

00:55:54.875 --> 00:55:55.708
The door!

00:56:08.791 --> 00:56:09.666
Sit anywhere you like.

00:56:14.541 --> 00:56:17.000
-Thank you for your flowers.
-Patterned socks?

00:56:17.416 --> 00:56:19.958
Stop it. You know I have a boyfriend.

00:56:20.583 --> 00:56:23.083
Although he is poor, selfish,

00:56:23.166 --> 00:56:24.833
stingy and old fashioned...

00:56:25.166 --> 00:56:26.375
She's not talking about me.

00:56:26.791 --> 00:56:28.291
He's still my boyfriend.

00:56:28.750 --> 00:56:30.000
I can't accept you.

00:56:30.625 --> 00:56:32.250
Hey, don't.

00:56:33.791 --> 00:56:34.625
Don't.

00:56:37.083 --> 00:56:37.916
Don't!

00:56:39.541 --> 00:56:41.166
I will kill you, bastard!

00:56:41.958 --> 00:56:42.791
It's you?

00:56:43.000 --> 00:56:43.833
It's you!

00:56:44.083 --> 00:56:44.916
It's you?

00:56:48.375 --> 00:56:49.250
Actually, I meant...

00:56:49.416 --> 00:56:51.125
I will kill you, bastard!

00:56:51.458 --> 00:56:52.708
Don't give her a hard time!

00:56:52.875 --> 00:56:53.875
Why are you holding a knife?

00:56:53.958 --> 00:56:56.125
-Put it down first.
-Wait, listen to me.

00:56:56.625 --> 00:56:58.166
I've followed you for a long time.

00:56:58.333 --> 00:56:59.833
It turns out you're here for this bitch!

00:56:59.916 --> 00:57:00.791
Me?

00:57:00.958 --> 00:57:03.041
Three fingers are pointing at you.
Why are you still asking?

00:57:03.541 --> 00:57:05.541
-How dare you try to steal
-I...

00:57:05.625 --> 00:57:07.708
-the wife of Million Wong?
-Well...

00:57:07.791 --> 00:57:08.708
-I...
-Let me ask you.

00:57:08.875 --> 00:57:10.166
Who do you love, her or me?

00:57:10.708 --> 00:57:12.083
I was just playing around.

00:57:12.583 --> 00:57:14.708
She was just playing around.

00:57:14.791 --> 00:57:17.583
You were played, you bitch.

00:57:18.000 --> 00:57:20.041
You embarrass your family.
You just want money, right?

00:57:20.125 --> 00:57:21.500
Fine, it's just money!

00:57:21.583 --> 00:57:23.166
Here.

00:57:24.458 --> 00:57:26.583
Here's some money.

00:57:26.791 --> 00:57:28.833
What? You got the money.
You still won't leave?

00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:30.250
You two...

00:57:30.416 --> 00:57:31.916
Fine, I am leaving!

00:57:32.125 --> 00:57:33.750
Man. Wait, Man.

00:57:33.833 --> 00:57:35.291
This is your home, where are you going?

00:57:35.458 --> 00:57:37.625
Yes, this is my home!

00:57:38.041 --> 00:57:39.916
You two, scram!

00:57:40.541 --> 00:57:42.875
-Scram!
-Man, don't be mad. Listen to me.

00:57:43.041 --> 00:57:44.875
What more do you want?
Wait for me downstairs.

00:57:45.125 --> 00:57:46.916
Let me teach this bitch a lesson.

00:57:47.083 --> 00:57:48.250
Go, what are you doing?

00:57:48.458 --> 00:57:49.291
Fine.

00:57:50.291 --> 00:57:51.625
I'm seriously warning you!

00:57:51.791 --> 00:57:53.375
Never see my wife again.

00:57:53.541 --> 00:57:56.250
Or I will beat you up
whenever I see you! Get it?

00:57:56.416 --> 00:57:59.416
She's gone. Why are you still acting?

00:57:59.833 --> 00:58:01.708
You were so happy to tell me off just now.

00:58:01.791 --> 00:58:03.125
That's how acting is.

00:58:03.333 --> 00:58:04.875
What do you think
of my performance just now?

00:58:05.000 --> 00:58:05.833
Bad.

00:58:06.000 --> 00:58:08.625
Are you kidding? I got a prize
for acting in a drama before.

00:58:08.708 --> 00:58:10.041
But you were really bad.

00:58:10.333 --> 00:58:11.250
I haven't asked you yet.

00:58:11.333 --> 00:58:13.083
Why would you let that woman court you?

00:58:14.250 --> 00:58:17.000
She is nice
and she always buys flowers from me.

00:58:17.166 --> 00:58:18.958
So we shop and have tea whenever I'm free.

00:58:19.125 --> 00:58:21.916
Who knew that she was a lesbian?

00:58:22.458 --> 00:58:23.583
I didn't expect that it was her.

00:58:24.166 --> 00:58:26.458
Hey, she is waiting for you downstairs.

00:58:26.541 --> 00:58:27.791
Aren't you going?

00:58:28.208 --> 00:58:29.125
Go!

00:58:29.291 --> 00:58:32.041
I will accompany you every day
after I solve this case, okay?

00:58:34.541 --> 00:58:35.750
I bought you something.

00:58:35.916 --> 00:58:37.000
Really? What is it?

00:58:37.208 --> 00:58:38.041
Patterned socks.

00:58:38.208 --> 00:58:39.041
Burn them.

00:58:47.208 --> 00:58:48.791
Mr. Wong, good morning.

00:58:49.375 --> 00:58:50.458
Good morning.

00:58:52.250 --> 00:58:54.166
Mr. Wong, good morning,
Mrs. Wong is not around.

00:58:54.250 --> 00:58:55.708
-I know.
-There's no power in there.

00:58:55.791 --> 00:58:58.291
It's fine.
I just want to get a cup of water.

00:59:19.416 --> 00:59:20.541
This arrived in the morning.

00:59:27.666 --> 00:59:28.583
What's the matter?

00:59:28.750 --> 00:59:30.083
Nothing, you may go.

00:59:31.291 --> 00:59:32.583
You must have a problem.

00:59:32.750 --> 00:59:34.666
I told you already.
It's none of your business anyway.

00:59:35.250 --> 00:59:36.208
Go.

00:59:40.750 --> 00:59:42.041
ATTENTION

00:59:43.708 --> 00:59:45.000
"Attention"?

00:59:50.541 --> 00:59:54.166
"Don't use a lighter to read."

00:59:54.791 --> 00:59:55.916
What does this mean?

01:00:04.291 --> 01:00:05.625
It's brandy.

01:00:18.875 --> 01:00:19.958
CALL ME. TAILOR.

01:00:34.500 --> 01:00:35.375
Boss.

01:00:39.208 --> 01:00:41.000
Hello, Tailor?

01:00:41.250 --> 01:00:42.208
How are you?

01:00:42.708 --> 01:00:44.000
How did you get my picture?

01:00:44.458 --> 01:00:45.916
Through a camera.

01:00:46.041 --> 01:00:47.000
I followed you for so long.

01:00:47.083 --> 01:00:49.458
But I didn't expect you
to court this one too.

01:00:49.583 --> 01:00:51.041
I think the gossip magazines

01:00:51.208 --> 01:00:53.625
would be very interested
in such hot pictures.

01:00:53.708 --> 01:00:56.666
-Beware of karma.
-I'll surely get my karma,

01:00:56.833 --> 01:00:59.500
so I need to save more money
for the future.

01:00:59.750 --> 01:01:02.250
If you want those nude pictures back,

01:01:02.333 --> 01:01:03.916
come to my office at seven.

01:01:04.000 --> 01:01:04.958
What do you want?

01:01:11.916 --> 01:01:13.041
Fire station, please.

01:01:14.458 --> 01:01:15.708
Tell me, what's the matter?

01:01:16.416 --> 01:01:18.833
This is the fire station.
Who is this? Speak.

01:01:20.416 --> 01:01:21.916
Are there any raincoats for sale? Thanks.

01:01:22.083 --> 01:01:23.791
Buy them at 7-11, you bastard!

01:01:24.208 --> 01:01:26.625
Bastard? What's with the attitude?
What's your ID number?

01:01:26.708 --> 01:01:29.541
-Don't hang up. Hello?
-Tailor, you are going too far!

01:01:30.250 --> 01:01:32.250
You will regret it if you don't come.

01:01:32.875 --> 01:01:34.750
That's all. Don't interrupt my exercise.

01:01:51.416 --> 01:01:52.500
Mr. Wong, what are you doing?

01:01:52.583 --> 01:01:54.416
I told you, I was drinking some water.

01:02:10.208 --> 01:02:14.083
You stepped on my supper!
You have to pay me!

01:02:32.833 --> 01:02:34.166
Miss, who are you looking for?

01:02:34.333 --> 01:02:35.666
I have an appointment with Mr. Tailor.

01:02:35.833 --> 01:02:36.958
Please follow me.

01:02:42.375 --> 01:02:43.250
Come in.

01:02:45.250 --> 01:02:46.083
Please come in.

01:02:50.333 --> 01:02:52.416
I am so happy to see you.

01:02:52.666 --> 01:02:55.083
Find the files for the first half
of the year. I won't take any calls.

01:02:55.250 --> 01:02:56.083
Okay.

01:02:59.000 --> 01:02:59.833
Take a seat.

01:03:03.708 --> 01:03:04.541
Cut the crap.

01:03:04.791 --> 01:03:06.791
How much do you want for the pictures?

01:03:07.583 --> 01:03:08.958
Please don't misunderstand.

01:03:09.250 --> 01:03:12.291
Even if I am not that rich,

01:03:12.541 --> 01:03:14.750
I'm not interested in 100 or 800 million.

01:03:14.958 --> 01:03:17.125
Do you think I'm blackmailing you?

01:03:17.541 --> 01:03:19.583
All right, name your price.

01:03:20.125 --> 01:03:23.541
We're friends.
It's not good to talk about money.

01:03:23.625 --> 01:03:26.583
Actually, I want to give you money.

01:03:26.833 --> 01:03:31.458
I've checked and confirmed that
your current husband is an impostor.

01:03:31.791 --> 01:03:34.333
I can kill him for you and leave no trace.

01:03:34.416 --> 01:03:38.541
And I will give you 300 million
for the land in Wan Chai.

01:03:40.041 --> 01:03:42.375
Go and rob a bank.
That land is worth two billion.

01:03:42.583 --> 01:03:44.875
Yes, I told you I'm not interested
in only 100 million.

01:03:45.041 --> 01:03:46.791
Two billion is more like it.

01:03:46.958 --> 01:03:48.083
Damn you!

01:03:48.250 --> 01:03:50.041
Don't speak foul language.

01:03:50.208 --> 01:03:52.208
If you do, it will damage your image

01:03:52.375 --> 01:03:54.416
as a pretty lesbian.

01:03:57.458 --> 01:03:58.625
You're despicable!

01:04:00.083 --> 01:04:01.708
-You...
-What?

01:04:02.041 --> 01:04:03.583
Go to the lawyer's office in three days.

01:04:03.666 --> 01:04:05.583
Or I will give out your pictures
in Portland Street

01:04:05.791 --> 01:04:07.375
and to the gossip magazines.

01:04:17.083 --> 01:04:18.625
Hey. What are you looking at?

01:04:18.708 --> 01:04:20.333
Why are you sneaking around?
Are you stealing?

01:04:20.416 --> 01:04:22.083
No, there is a beautiful naked girl.

01:04:22.708 --> 01:04:23.583
I don't trust you.

01:04:23.666 --> 01:04:25.083
Come and take a look.

01:04:25.666 --> 01:04:28.333
What if you attack me after I look?

01:04:28.958 --> 01:04:31.000
Even if you don't come here,
I'll still attack you.

01:04:34.500 --> 01:04:35.333
What happened?

01:04:35.500 --> 01:04:37.375
I was attacked by a man in a suit.

01:04:37.458 --> 01:04:38.625
Hurry, let's chase after him.

01:04:40.625 --> 01:04:41.875
Have you seen a man in a suit?

01:04:42.541 --> 01:04:43.666
This way.

01:04:45.625 --> 01:04:47.250
Thief!

01:04:49.916 --> 01:04:51.083
What noise is that?

01:04:52.625 --> 01:04:54.166
Was there a noise? I don't think so.

01:04:54.458 --> 01:04:56.166
I will break his head if I see him.

01:04:56.458 --> 01:04:57.833
Go that way. I will stand guard here.

01:05:07.166 --> 01:05:08.125
You...

01:05:10.875 --> 01:05:13.208
Pervert! Help!

01:05:14.541 --> 01:05:15.541
This way.

01:05:17.041 --> 01:05:18.791
I changed jobs!
Why are you still bothering me?

01:05:18.875 --> 01:05:20.666
-Arrest him!
-Scram, you bitch!

01:05:40.958 --> 01:05:42.041
Give...

01:05:42.125 --> 01:05:43.458
Give me back my teeth.

01:06:11.791 --> 01:06:14.708
Hey, it's you! This is new.

01:06:14.875 --> 01:06:16.250
How is it new?

01:06:19.166 --> 01:06:20.541
Guess who killed me?

01:06:20.625 --> 01:06:21.791
Who?

01:06:23.458 --> 01:06:24.875
Hey, give me some hints.

01:06:31.333 --> 01:06:32.166
It's her.

01:07:05.666 --> 01:07:07.708
You jerk, you're interrupting. Go away!

01:07:22.958 --> 01:07:24.250
You jerk, it's not 1997 yet.

01:07:24.333 --> 01:07:26.458
How dare you give me Chinese yuan?
Do you think I am blind?

01:07:26.541 --> 01:07:27.375
Die!

01:07:39.791 --> 01:07:40.625
You're back.

01:07:43.958 --> 01:07:46.333
You're panting. Where did you go?

01:07:46.875 --> 01:07:48.333
Let me ask you. Where have you been?

01:07:48.583 --> 01:07:50.625
Where have I been?
I've been playing mahjong all night.

01:07:50.708 --> 01:07:52.791
-What do you think?
-You were playing mahjong all night?

01:07:52.875 --> 01:07:54.166
We've played 16 rounds already.

01:07:54.791 --> 01:07:56.208
Is something wrong with your husband?

01:07:56.833 --> 01:07:58.625
Of course.

01:07:59.041 --> 01:08:02.208
Why are you dressed that way?
Where have you been?

01:08:03.458 --> 01:08:05.000
What is this?

01:08:07.458 --> 01:08:08.500
It's blood!

01:08:08.708 --> 01:08:09.916
Did you kill someone?

01:08:17.250 --> 01:08:19.458
What's wrong with you?

01:08:21.416 --> 01:08:24.708
We're husband and wife.
Can't I joke with you?

01:08:24.916 --> 01:08:27.208
The day after tomorrow
will be our seventh anniversary.

01:08:27.375 --> 01:08:28.791
I want to throw a party to celebrate.

01:08:28.875 --> 01:08:30.250
Okay?

01:08:30.916 --> 01:08:34.125
Gosh, you're still mad.

01:08:34.625 --> 01:08:35.791
Let me give you a kiss.

01:09:01.958 --> 01:09:03.083
You scared me.

01:09:04.458 --> 01:09:05.916
Officer Lai, help yourself.

01:09:20.458 --> 01:09:21.875
Do you know Tailor Lam was killed?

01:09:23.291 --> 01:09:24.250
I do.

01:09:24.541 --> 01:09:25.916
Do you know that I'm going to die soon?

01:09:26.291 --> 01:09:27.375
I do.

01:09:27.541 --> 01:09:29.708
If you can't find the murderer,
you'll die soon too.

01:09:30.458 --> 01:09:32.500
I am 90 percent sure who the murderer is.

01:09:33.041 --> 01:09:33.958
Who exactly is it?

01:09:34.125 --> 01:09:34.958
Don't be anxious.

01:09:35.500 --> 01:09:38.333
My seventh sense tells me
that we will get the answer tonight.

01:09:40.708 --> 01:09:43.625
The real murderer
will reveal his evil side tonight.

01:09:50.250 --> 01:09:51.375
Don't move! Hands on your head!

01:09:53.041 --> 01:09:54.291
It's you?

01:09:54.875 --> 01:09:56.916
Mr. Wong, I want to tell you something.

01:09:59.791 --> 01:10:00.791
I know what to do.

01:10:00.958 --> 01:10:02.958
Excuse me, everyone. Please go over there.

01:10:03.125 --> 01:10:04.791
Thank you for your cooperation. I'm sorry.

01:10:05.166 --> 01:10:06.041
Please go over there.

01:10:07.083 --> 01:10:08.416
They left. You may speak now.

01:10:09.041 --> 01:10:10.625
I wanted you to leave.

01:10:12.958 --> 01:10:15.291
You should have told me earlier.
I have my pride.

01:10:19.791 --> 01:10:21.541
Mr. Wong, take care of Judy.

01:10:21.958 --> 01:10:22.875
What's up with Judy?

01:10:23.083 --> 01:10:25.541
It has nothing to do with her.

01:10:25.750 --> 01:10:26.833
Speak clearly.

01:10:27.000 --> 01:10:28.541
I don't have a choice but to tell you now.

01:10:28.625 --> 01:10:30.166
Actually, she...

01:10:30.333 --> 01:10:31.875
What? Be frank, tell me!

01:10:32.083 --> 01:10:34.416
Yes, be frank and speak up.

01:10:36.708 --> 01:10:39.375
I love this song. Dance with me, come on.

01:10:48.083 --> 01:10:49.000
Mr. Wong.

01:11:00.583 --> 01:11:03.041
We throw a party every year,
but I am the happiest this year.

01:11:03.625 --> 01:11:04.583
How about you?

01:11:05.125 --> 01:11:08.083
That's great, as long as you're happy.

01:11:08.958 --> 01:11:10.916
Why does it seem like
you're not very happy?

01:11:12.125 --> 01:11:13.333
What do you think?

01:11:16.083 --> 01:11:19.791
Everyone does things for a reason.

01:11:22.583 --> 01:11:25.083
But I think there's karma for everything

01:11:25.458 --> 01:11:27.208
that everyone has done.

01:11:32.333 --> 01:11:34.125
Then what's the reason
for killing someone?

01:11:36.458 --> 01:11:37.958
Tell me, Judy!

01:11:50.333 --> 01:11:51.333
Why aren't you talking?

01:11:52.958 --> 01:11:53.916
Nothing.

01:11:54.000 --> 01:11:56.791
I am thinking that it would be great

01:11:57.250 --> 01:11:58.583
if you really were Million Wong.

01:11:59.541 --> 01:12:00.833
You know I am an impostor?

01:12:01.750 --> 01:12:04.375
I knew the first day I met you.

01:12:05.000 --> 01:12:06.458
You haven't answered my question.

01:12:07.958 --> 01:12:10.166
Don't make me dislike you.

01:12:12.375 --> 01:12:15.833
Million and I weren't happy
in recent years.

01:12:17.791 --> 01:12:19.000
The past few days,

01:12:19.875 --> 01:12:22.458
you helped me remember
the sweet memory of our love.

01:12:24.458 --> 01:12:26.125
We were poor back then.

01:12:26.916 --> 01:12:28.333
But our love was true.

01:12:29.416 --> 01:12:31.291
But after he got rich,

01:12:32.375 --> 01:12:34.083
he fooled around.

01:12:35.625 --> 01:12:36.708
And I...

01:12:37.750 --> 01:12:39.083
became more and more perverted.

01:12:40.625 --> 01:12:42.041
I hate being a woman.

01:12:43.208 --> 01:12:44.541
I want to be a man.

01:12:45.583 --> 01:12:47.583
A man who can compete with him for women.

01:12:49.708 --> 01:12:51.541
But after you came here,

01:12:52.125 --> 01:12:54.416
you made me feel like a woman again.

01:12:58.541 --> 01:13:00.458
I don't want to know who you are.

01:13:03.250 --> 01:13:04.916
I was just wondering...

01:13:06.000 --> 01:13:10.041
if you can play your role
wholeheartedly tonight.

01:13:16.166 --> 01:13:17.208
Honey.

01:13:21.666 --> 01:13:23.250
I want you to be with me tonight.

01:13:24.958 --> 01:13:26.291
Okay?

01:13:55.583 --> 01:13:56.791
I'll touch up my makeup first.

01:14:16.583 --> 01:14:19.000
You didn't finish talking earlier.
Who do you suspect is the murderer?

01:14:19.875 --> 01:14:20.916
I suspect it's Judy.

01:14:21.083 --> 01:14:22.333
How come?

01:14:22.541 --> 01:14:24.666
Actually, I was present
when Tailor was killed.

01:14:24.916 --> 01:14:26.125
I followed Judy there.

01:14:26.375 --> 01:14:29.375
Although I didn't witness her kill him,
no one else was around.

01:14:29.458 --> 01:14:30.916
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

01:14:31.083 --> 01:14:33.375
-Tell me.
-I don't know the reason.

01:14:33.458 --> 01:14:34.583
Are you kidding me?

01:14:34.666 --> 01:14:35.791
Wait, listen to me.

01:14:35.958 --> 01:14:38.250
Even if Judy killed someone,
I'm sure she had a reason.

01:14:38.416 --> 01:14:40.500
What reason? She murdered someone!

01:14:40.708 --> 01:14:41.833
You are a cop.

01:14:42.000 --> 01:14:44.083
-Don't really take her as your wife!
-Mr. Wong!

01:14:44.250 --> 01:14:46.291
-Long time no see.
-Good morning.

01:14:46.375 --> 01:14:47.250
I won't bother you.

01:14:50.583 --> 01:14:52.125
Tell me what else you know.

01:14:53.416 --> 01:14:54.750
I think she'll kill again.

01:14:54.958 --> 01:14:55.958
What?

01:14:56.125 --> 01:14:57.708
Kill those who know her secret.

01:14:58.791 --> 01:15:00.416
-Good thing I don't know it.
-Now you do.

01:15:00.583 --> 01:15:01.416
I know it too.

01:15:01.583 --> 01:15:03.166
Another person knows. Ms. Cheng!

01:15:03.333 --> 01:15:05.916
Go and inform her.
I will set up traps to arrest her.

01:15:06.083 --> 01:15:07.041
Go!

01:15:17.041 --> 01:15:18.041
It's me.

01:15:18.125 --> 01:15:19.708
-You scared me.
-Don't be like this.

01:15:19.916 --> 01:15:21.916
I have the most wonderful idea.
With this human skin mask,

01:15:22.083 --> 01:15:23.958
the murderer will faint once he sees me.

01:15:24.125 --> 01:15:25.458
Then I will arrest him right away.

01:15:26.375 --> 01:15:27.375
I'll put on the mask first.

01:15:29.125 --> 01:15:30.041
Hello!

01:15:32.250 --> 01:15:33.541
-What's wrong?
-You scared everyone!

01:15:33.791 --> 01:15:35.083
They read the newspapers, you idiot!

01:15:35.541 --> 01:15:36.416
What should we do now?

01:15:36.583 --> 01:15:38.875
Go to Judy's room and monitor her.
I'm sure you'll find something.

01:15:38.958 --> 01:15:39.791
I will?

01:15:40.208 --> 01:15:41.208
Where is my gun?

01:15:41.625 --> 01:15:43.250
It's dangerous.
You want me to return your gun?

01:15:43.333 --> 01:15:44.708
-Do you really think I'm an idiot?
-Hey.

01:15:49.791 --> 01:15:51.708
We must avenge Tailor tonight.

01:15:51.875 --> 01:15:54.916
He was obviously killed
by Million Wong and his wife.

01:15:55.416 --> 01:15:57.833
You two should be careful.

01:15:58.541 --> 01:15:59.500
Don't worry.

01:16:03.625 --> 01:16:04.541
Please come in.

01:16:04.833 --> 01:16:05.666
Please come in.

01:16:37.000 --> 01:16:38.416
So you have another boyfriend.

01:16:38.750 --> 01:16:40.625
-Don't come to see me again.
-It's a misunderstanding.

01:16:52.083 --> 01:16:53.541
Maybe this is a new dance move.

01:16:53.625 --> 01:16:54.708
Let's follow him.

01:16:59.291 --> 01:17:00.541
Miss, can we dance?

01:17:05.875 --> 01:17:06.833
Come here.

01:17:07.416 --> 01:17:09.000
Ms. Cheng, you're in danger.

01:17:09.375 --> 01:17:11.708
What? It's you again, pervert.

01:17:12.916 --> 01:17:14.666
I changed so many jobs because of you.

01:17:14.833 --> 01:17:16.625
I can't even escape from you
at this party!

01:17:18.125 --> 01:17:19.458
This is fate!

01:17:19.583 --> 01:17:21.500
-Come and rape me.
-It's a misunderstanding.

01:17:22.041 --> 01:17:23.666
Wait. Come on.

01:17:23.750 --> 01:17:25.625
Just once and never bother me again.

01:17:25.791 --> 01:17:27.583
Come and rape me!

01:17:32.750 --> 01:17:34.083
The victim died so horribly!

01:17:34.166 --> 01:17:36.583
-Right.
-Isn't it a heart attack?

01:17:38.000 --> 01:17:40.083
-What is it?
-A person was shot by an arrow.

01:17:42.583 --> 01:17:43.583
That's him.

01:17:43.875 --> 01:17:45.708
Don't move. The cops are coming.

01:17:47.208 --> 01:17:48.625
I monitored Judy Tong upstairs earlier.

01:17:48.708 --> 01:17:50.000
She hasn't left her room.

01:17:55.208 --> 01:17:56.208
We were set up.

01:18:13.250 --> 01:18:14.416
I don't want to be controlled.

01:18:14.750 --> 01:18:16.000
I know what I'm doing.

01:18:16.416 --> 01:18:18.208
Judy, this won't do you any good.

01:18:18.291 --> 01:18:20.125
-Don't ruin my plans.
-Judy!

01:18:20.583 --> 01:18:22.625
Scram. I don't want
to see you again tonight.

01:18:35.041 --> 01:18:36.000
It's you?

01:18:37.416 --> 01:18:39.916
I found a weapon
and wanted to show it to you.

01:18:40.000 --> 01:18:41.458
Must you hit me so hard?

01:18:48.166 --> 01:18:49.166
Freeze!

01:18:55.125 --> 01:18:56.708
-Judy.
-Don't do it!

01:18:57.625 --> 01:18:58.958
I know you are the murderer.

01:19:00.125 --> 01:19:02.625
Yes, I killed them all.

01:19:09.416 --> 01:19:10.625
Here's your gun.

01:19:11.083 --> 01:19:12.666
Good job, you'll be promoted.

01:19:12.750 --> 01:19:14.333
-Promoted to what?
-What do you think?

01:19:14.916 --> 01:19:16.208
Let's calculate my salary first.

01:19:16.500 --> 01:19:18.583
-Fine, go ahead.
-Let's go.

01:19:19.000 --> 01:19:22.333
-Give way, please.
-Give way, please.

01:19:32.875 --> 01:19:35.166
I'm leaving, honey.

01:20:21.875 --> 01:20:22.875
What are you doing?

01:20:26.083 --> 01:20:27.750
You don't know what happened earlier.

01:20:28.416 --> 01:20:29.625
What happened?

01:20:30.166 --> 01:20:32.041
Do you know that the murderer
has been arrested?

01:20:32.208 --> 01:20:33.666
Really? Who is the murderer?

01:20:33.833 --> 01:20:36.375
-It turns out the murderer is--
-Judy, right?

01:20:36.458 --> 01:20:38.500
She flirted with you
before she was taken away.

01:20:38.583 --> 01:20:40.708
She even kissed your left armpit.

01:20:40.791 --> 01:20:42.666
How did I know? My cousin told me.

01:20:44.791 --> 01:20:46.208
That's totally wrong.

01:20:47.666 --> 01:20:48.833
Totally wrong!

01:20:49.291 --> 01:20:51.208
-Do you dare to deny it?
-I don't.

01:20:51.375 --> 01:20:52.833
But she didn't kiss my left armpit.

01:20:52.916 --> 01:20:54.083
Where did she kiss you then?

01:20:56.625 --> 01:20:59.750
Man, trust me. I only love you.

01:20:59.958 --> 01:21:02.500
I am willing to take
any punishment from you.

01:21:02.833 --> 01:21:04.125
Come on, punish me.

01:21:05.750 --> 01:21:07.458
Who has the time to punish you?

01:21:08.791 --> 01:21:10.125
Then I will punish you.

01:21:15.375 --> 01:21:17.541
-You are so bad.
-You're hitting me?

01:21:21.833 --> 01:21:22.708
Come on.

01:21:31.208 --> 01:21:32.583
Where did you get this from?

01:21:32.666 --> 01:21:34.375
You told me to punish you.

01:21:34.708 --> 01:21:36.125
Can't I?

01:21:52.125 --> 01:21:53.291
Are you scared?

01:21:55.000 --> 01:21:56.750
I'm really scared.

01:21:57.125 --> 01:21:59.125
Do you dare to let others kiss you again?

01:21:59.625 --> 01:22:00.625
Do you?

01:22:09.041 --> 01:22:11.250
Untie me first.

01:22:12.041 --> 01:22:13.125
Hey.

01:22:19.083 --> 01:22:21.166
-What are you doing?
-Taking a shower.

01:22:39.875 --> 01:22:41.375
Let's not waste any time.

01:22:43.791 --> 01:22:46.208
Honey, come over quickly.

01:22:49.208 --> 01:22:50.208
It's stuck.

01:22:51.000 --> 01:22:52.041
Punish me.

01:23:02.041 --> 01:23:03.625
What? It's you?

01:23:03.791 --> 01:23:04.958
You are too nosy!

01:23:05.666 --> 01:23:07.208
Man!

01:23:07.291 --> 01:23:08.500
You dragged Judy down.

01:23:09.541 --> 01:23:10.916
What? Say that again.

01:23:11.000 --> 01:23:12.458
I want to take revenge for Judy!

01:23:12.833 --> 01:23:15.125
I can't hear clearly.
Say that again. What revenge?

01:23:15.208 --> 01:23:17.250
I said I want to take revenge for Judy.

01:23:17.333 --> 01:23:18.875
I can't hear clearly. Can you repeat that?

01:23:18.958 --> 01:23:20.166
Are you making fun of me?

01:23:27.708 --> 01:23:28.833
You want to peep?

01:23:30.833 --> 01:23:31.750
Dragon Tail Swing!

01:23:31.833 --> 01:23:33.458
-Swing all you want!
-Don't!

01:23:36.958 --> 01:23:38.083
I'm going to crush you!

01:23:51.875 --> 01:23:53.250
Damn it, you poked me so many times.

01:23:53.333 --> 01:23:55.208
Are you serious? Damn you!

01:23:56.125 --> 01:23:58.583
I didn't poke you. I stabbed you!

01:24:06.500 --> 01:24:07.666
What are you looking at?

01:24:08.166 --> 01:24:09.541
I'm going to kill you!

01:24:13.000 --> 01:24:14.291
No way.

01:24:15.000 --> 01:24:16.375
That has nothing to do with me.

01:24:17.333 --> 01:24:18.333
I know!

01:24:33.083 --> 01:24:34.250
Are you done?

01:24:34.833 --> 01:24:36.083
It's my turn now.

01:24:39.041 --> 01:24:40.000
Not exactly!

01:24:44.166 --> 01:24:45.250
Thank you.

01:25:01.708 --> 01:25:03.291
You think I am useless.

01:25:05.916 --> 01:25:07.750
I am having cramps.

01:25:10.833 --> 01:25:14.666
These are the pictures Tailor Lam took
of Judy Tong and Cheng Man-ching.

01:25:22.708 --> 01:25:24.833
Cheng Man-ching is not only a lesbian.

01:25:25.083 --> 01:25:26.541
She is psychotic too.

01:25:26.791 --> 01:25:28.416
She has a strong inclination to violence.

01:25:28.791 --> 01:25:30.750
She wants to kill everyone who loves Judy

01:25:30.916 --> 01:25:32.625
and everyone who harms Judy.

01:25:32.958 --> 01:25:34.333
So she killed Million Wong first.

01:25:34.666 --> 01:25:35.791
Then she killed Tailor.

01:25:36.083 --> 01:25:38.083
Judy made a statement
about what happened that night.

01:25:39.416 --> 01:25:41.500
You can't fall for that fake Million Wong!

01:25:41.833 --> 01:25:43.125
I don't want to be controlled.

01:25:43.333 --> 01:25:44.500
I know what I'm doing.

01:25:44.583 --> 01:25:46.083
That fake Million Wong should die...

01:25:46.916 --> 01:25:49.458
so that you and I
can have a bright future.

01:25:49.875 --> 01:25:50.958
You are crazy.

01:25:51.250 --> 01:25:52.250
I'm crazy?

01:25:52.875 --> 01:25:54.375
You've had a change of heart.

01:25:55.000 --> 01:25:56.166
Million beat you up.

01:25:56.333 --> 01:25:58.250
I took revenge for you, so I killed him.

01:25:58.875 --> 01:26:01.125
-You killed Million?
-So what?

01:26:01.541 --> 01:26:03.250
I killed Tailor too.

01:26:04.000 --> 01:26:05.250
You think I don't know.

01:26:05.416 --> 01:26:07.833
He took our naked pictures
to blackmail you.

01:26:08.375 --> 01:26:11.375
Such rubbish needs to be killed,
so that we won't be threatened.

01:26:12.958 --> 01:26:14.708
So it was you all along.

01:26:15.916 --> 01:26:16.875
Why?

01:26:17.041 --> 01:26:19.583
I did everything for your sake.

01:26:21.083 --> 01:26:22.666
I'm going to kill him now.

01:26:24.541 --> 01:26:25.916
I won't let you do so.

01:26:26.500 --> 01:26:27.666
Did you fall for that man?

01:26:27.916 --> 01:26:28.791
Get lost!

01:26:29.541 --> 01:26:31.125
No!

01:26:34.375 --> 01:26:37.041
That's why she wanted
to kill me that night too.

01:26:38.541 --> 01:26:41.125
Cheng Man-ching was the one
who wanted to shoot me with an arrow?

01:26:45.125 --> 01:26:47.416
Why would Judy protect Cheng Man-ching?

01:26:47.833 --> 01:26:49.500
She has a deep affection for her.

01:26:49.750 --> 01:26:52.125
So she acted on impulse
and took all the blame.

01:26:54.541 --> 01:26:55.791
She is really...

01:26:56.250 --> 01:26:59.083
Really what?
It's none of your business, right?

01:26:59.250 --> 01:27:00.125
Yes.

01:27:00.291 --> 01:27:01.166
That's good.

01:27:01.333 --> 01:27:02.500
You have done a great job.

01:27:02.666 --> 01:27:04.166
You have another undercover case.

01:27:04.375 --> 01:27:06.083
-What?
-Are you kidding me?

01:27:08.000 --> 01:27:09.041
An order?

01:27:09.541 --> 01:27:10.375
You...

01:27:10.625 --> 01:27:12.416
Be polite, call me Commandant Lek.

01:27:12.625 --> 01:27:15.083
ICAC admitted their mistake
and withdrew their charges against me.

01:27:15.166 --> 01:27:16.375
I have resumed duty now.

01:27:16.625 --> 01:27:17.750
Is that true?

01:27:18.291 --> 01:27:19.250
Of course.

01:27:19.541 --> 01:27:20.708
What's the big deal?

01:27:20.916 --> 01:27:23.291
-You have the same rank as me.
-You are wrong.

01:27:23.541 --> 01:27:25.208
The boss said that
you always beat people up.

01:27:25.416 --> 01:27:26.875
You are suspended now.

01:27:27.125 --> 01:27:29.916
So I don't need to wait until 1997
before I deal with you.

01:27:30.125 --> 01:27:32.125
-You dare to hit me?
-So what?

01:27:32.208 --> 01:27:33.916
No! Stop!

01:27:34.083 --> 01:27:37.583
-What are you doing? Let me go.
-Stop! Hey!

01:27:38.208 --> 01:27:40.500
Don't stop them. Just let them be.

01:27:40.583 --> 01:27:42.083
Chow Sing-sing,
someone is looking for you.

01:27:59.500 --> 01:28:00.583
Hey, Big Mouth.

01:28:03.166 --> 01:28:05.416
It's you, Big Nose. Are you all right?

01:28:05.500 --> 01:28:07.916
Why wouldn't I be?
We are having a party tonight.

01:28:08.541 --> 01:28:10.166
I've invited many girls.

01:28:12.416 --> 01:28:13.625
Why are you still standing there?

01:28:13.791 --> 01:28:15.958
-Go and invite some boys.
-Yes, hurry up.

01:28:16.708 --> 01:28:18.291
Okay, I'll make it next time.

01:28:18.541 --> 01:28:20.458
-Enjoy yourselves.
-Okay!

01:28:23.875 --> 01:28:25.791
Wait for me!
